      "type": "SLIDE",
      "title": "The Survival Guide to Marriage",
      "contentMarkdown": "## Birthday funroot\nReordered from easy warm-up to couple jokes to husband-survival jokes to final punchline questions.\n\nFor custom punchlines, option D stays at the bottom and the reveal is preserved in each host prompt.",
      "mediaUrl": null,
      "background": "/backgrounds/marriage-survival-guide-birthday/slide-intro.webp"
